{"id":1559,"category_slug":"toeic","category_name":"TOEIC Listening","position":347,"title":"Conversation 177","subtitle":"Buying Paintbrushes at Store","level":"B1","parts":18,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/toeic/conversation-177.1559/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-177-2024-09-14-18-34-50/0-conversation-177.mp3","transcript":"Welcome to Chapman Store.\nIs there anything that I can help you with today?\nHi, I'm looking for paintbrushes for my nephew.\nDo you mean those with large handles for kids?\nHmm... I'm not sure if we have them in stock.\nNot really, no.\nIt's more of a paintbrush set for beginners.\nAs far as I know, we only have those sets for professionals.\nBut let me check in the back.\nHey, John, do we have beginner paintbrush kits?\nYeah, we do, but not on this floor.\nI think they're in the basement.\nLet me show you.\nFantastic.\nIs there any way I can get them gift-wrapped?\nI'm pretty bad at that.\nActually, the gift-wrapping service comes free with any purchase at our store.\nThat's awesome. Thanks!","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T21:02:47","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"Welcome to Chapman Store.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-177-2024-09-14-18-34-50/1.mp3","time_start":0.2,"time_end":1.79},{"position":2,"content":"Is there anything that I can help you with today?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-177-2024-09-14-18-34-50/2.mp3","time_start":1.79,"time_end":4.21},{"position":3,"content":"Hi, I'm looking for paintbrushes for my nephew.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-177-2024-09-14-18-34-50/3.mp3","time_start":4.21,"time_end":7.39},{"position":4,"content":"Do you mean those with large handles for kids?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-177-2024-09-14-18-34-50/4.mp3","time_start":7.39,"time_end":10.24},{"position":5,"conte